---
title: Cheesy Harissa Chickpea Taquitos with Baby Leaf Salad
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Cheesy Harissa Chickpea Taquitos in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal. Meaning 'little taco', taquitos are one of the original Cal-Mex dishes, known for their crispy rolled up shells and tasty fillings.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R17_W27_UK_QV23454-3_Main_high-a608ac58.jpg
